!!!! Commit [[3385bde|https://github.com/CrossEye/TW5-SimpleOutlinePlugin/commit/3385bde6a9fdb502eaa82947a9f480fcdf98228d]] (2026-04-12)

```
group-template, header-template, tiddler-link; two new demos

* Add group-template attribute — full TW widget power inside group <summary>
  elements; receives so-label only (no currentTiddler for group nodes)
* Add header-template attribute — replaces default <h2> in !! section headers;
  receives so-label only
* Add tiddler-link / tiddler-link-label attributes — adds a link inline after
  each tiddler item's label; opens the tiddler without toggling the node via
  stopPropagation; visible in both collapsed and expanded states
* Fix summary arrow alignment for multi-line labels: align-items: flex-start
  plus margin-top: 0.2em on .so-arrow pins the arrow to the first-line midpoint
* Add Tiddler Link Demo: shows tiddler-link + open-depth together
* Add Styled Outline Demo: shows group-template and header-template; group
  template conditionally renders a description field from a matching tiddler
* Update Simple Outline Plugin overview: full attribute table, new demo sections
```

